p_rec.program_details['cost'] = 'WEEKDAYS: Fees can start as low as $430 for single woman with or without children (on a case-by-case basis will adjust payments depending on the financial needs). For housing, must have a source of income at time of entry or be vouchered in by an agency. WEEKENDS: None. NOTE: See Program Description for further information regarding weekend and weekday admission and fee policies.'
